snippet.title: Arcade Game: Dorodon (1983 UPL (Falcon License))
snippet.description:
A maze game where you must change all lines to white colors.

Note: Cheats were used in this game. Change the date to 1983 since it says in the title screen. The game is endless. I killed myself afterwards after repeating levels are shown.
